{
  "chapter": 79,
  "chapter_summary": "第七十九回「山君夫人」。江玉郎挟持铁心兰，与铁萍姑亲热，铁心兰在地室中发现黑蜘蛛与慕容九妹亦被囚禁。花无缺为白夫人解开锁链，白夫人百般挑逗，花无缺不为所动。白夫人丈夫白山君突然出现，怒斥花无缺与其妻有染，二人激战。白夫人趁机以游丝针暗算花无缺，随即扑入白山君怀中表忠心。花无缺中毒针倒地，白山君却为他吸出暗器，揭露真相：白夫人有受虐癖，故意激怒丈夫以求虐待。白山君自报家门为十二星相之虎，以笑腰穴游丝针要挟花无缺交出移花接玉秘笈，花无缺断然拒绝，白山君佯装离去却在暗中监控。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "text": "你真是会多心，有了你这么漂亮的老婆，我还会打别人的主意么？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 4,
      "line_end": 4
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_ping_gu",
      "speaker_name": "铁萍姑",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你知道，你不但是我平生第一个男人，也是平生第一个对我如此亲切的人，无论你这么做是真是假，只要你永远这样对待我，我就已心满意足了，你就算做别的坏事，我……我也……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是个多么寂寞的女人，又是个多么可怜的女人，她甚至已明知江玉郎对她是假的，假的她竟也接受，她难道已再也不能忍受孤独……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "这里也有个你的老朋友，是么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 36,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "蜘蛛兄，又有位朋友来看你了，你为什么不理人家？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 42,
      "line_end": 42
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "speaker_name": "黑蜘蛛",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "你……你怎地也来了？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 44
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_hei_zhi_zhu",
      "text": "我们本来……本来是想来助你一臂之力的。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 48,
      "line_end": 48
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "只可惜普天之下，只怕谁也救不了你们。",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 52,
      "line_end": 52
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "speaker_name": "铁心兰",
      "listener": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "text": "你莫忘了，还有花公子……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 54,
      "line_end": 54
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_jiang_yu_lang",
      "speaker_name": "江玉郎",
      "listener": "char_tie_xin_lan",
      "text": "花无缺此刻还等着别人去救他哩！",
      "tone": "狂笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 56,
      "line_end": 56
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人现在可以起来了么？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 60,
      "line_end": 60
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我现在怎么站得起来？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 62,
      "line_end": 62
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "怎会站不起来？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 64,
      "line_end": 64
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "呆子，你难道看不出来，我现在简直连一丝力气都没有。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 66,
      "line_end": 66
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "痒……痒死我了，原来你也不是好人，故意来逗我。",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 76,
      "line_end": 76
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "在下绝非有意。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 78,
      "line_end": 78
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "谁知道你是不是有意的！",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 80,
      "line_end": 80
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人再不起来，在下就要……",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 82,
      "line_end": 82
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "呆子，你这么大一个男人，遇见这么点小事就没主意了么？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 86,
      "line_end": 86
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人的意思要在下怎样？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 90
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你扶不起我来，难道还抱不起我来么？",
      "tone": "娇声",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 92,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人此刻若真的站不起来，在下就在这里等等好了。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 100,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我若是一个时辰都站不起来呢？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "在下素来很沉得住气。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 106,
      "line_end": 106
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我若是三天三夜都站不起来，你难道等三天三夜？",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 108,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "在下知道夫人绝不会让在下等三天三夜的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不好，我……我丈夫回来了。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "夫人，你……",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "在哪里？",
      "tone": "焦急",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 120
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "在……就在……",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 122,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "就在这里！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "臭婊子，看你做的什么事？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好个不中用的东西，我要你看着这臭女人，你却只知道睡懒觉。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 138
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "阁下暂且息怒，听我一言……",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我听你什么？我听你个屁，老子前脚一走，你们这双狗男女就不干好事。老子早就知道这臭婊子是天生的贱货，竟会看上你这种小兔崽子。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "老实告诉你，我们在一起已经有两三年了，只要你一出去，我们就亲亲热热地在一起，你又能怎么样？",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 148,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "气死我了！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 150,
      "line_end": 150
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "白……白夫人，我和你无冤无仇，你……你为何要如此？……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 152,
      "line_end": 152
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好人，你怕什么？事情反正已到这种地步了，咱们不如索性跟他讲个清楚反而好，是么？",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 154,
      "line_end": 154
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "text": "你……你……",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 156,
      "line_end": 156
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "讲清楚也没用，你们这对狗男女若想要老子做睁眼王八，那是在做梦！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 160
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好小子，难怪敢偷人家的老婆，原来有两下子！",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "对，不要怕他，为了我，你也该和他拼了。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "好人，我真还未看出你有这么好的功夫，有你这样的情郎，我还怕什么？你赶紧宰了这老家伙，我们就可以安安稳稳地做一对永远夫妻了。",
      "tone": "欣喜",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哎哟，小心他下一着虎爪抓心！",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_fu_ren",
      "speaker_name": "白夫人",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "我本来以为已爱上了别人，但你们一打起来，我才知道真正爱的还是你，我宁可将天下的男人都杀光，也不能看别人动你一根手指。",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你现在总该知道咱老婆的厉害了吧？谁若沾上她，不倒霉才怪，你年纪轻轻，不像个呆子，怎地偏偏做出这种事来？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你……你想于什么？",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我那老婆暗器之歹毒，昔年连燕南天听了都有些头疼，你两条腿各中一枚，我若不用这吸铁星将它吸出来，你这辈子就休想走路了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 246,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你……你为何要救我？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你以为我真相信我老婆的话么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "你既不信她的话，方才为何……为何要那般恼怒？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "小伙子，我知道你也被弄糊涂了，好生坐下来听我说吧！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "在下倒的确想请教请教。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 264,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你可知道，世上有一种奇怪的人，别人若是爱她敬她，她就觉得痛苦，若是百般凌辱虐待于她，她反而会觉得舒服快乐。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 268
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "世上真有这样的人？",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 270
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "自然是有的，我老婆就是其中的一个。",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 274
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "她……她怎会这样子的？",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 276,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "据说她从小就是如此，非但从小就喜欢别人虐待她，而且她自己还要虐待自己。到了老年时，这脾气更是变本加厉，竟连普通居室都待不下去，非要将住处布置成马厩一般，而且还要我用铁链锁住她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 280,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "原来这竟是她自愿如此的，在下本还以为……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 284
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我虽然知道她这毛病，但有时还是不忍下手，也不愿意动手，所以她就时常会故意激怒我，为的就是想让我揍她。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 286,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "今日之事，想来也必定就是为了这原故了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "她年华逐渐老去，总以为我会对她日久生厌，移情别恋，所以时常又会故意令我嫉妒……",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 292,
      "line_end": 292
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "其实白夫人那些做作全都是多余的，阁下爱妻之心，自始至终，从来也未曾改变过，是么？",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 294,
      "line_end": 294
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，我只顾了她的欢喜，却令朋友你吃了个大亏，此事实在是我夫妻之错，是打是罚，但凭朋友你吩咐如何？",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 298,
      "line_end": 298
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "实不相瞒，在下本来对此事也委实有些恼怒，但听了阁下这番话，却非但对阁下的处境甚是同情，对阁下如此深挚的伉俪之情，更是十分相敬。何况，在下本已作了贤伉俪的阶下囚，本只有任凭阁下处治的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 302,
      "line_end": 302
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "阁下又何苦要在我腰边暗施手脚？",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "真的么？那想必是我方才为你拔针时，一不小心，又将那游丝针插入你腰边什么穴道里去了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 308,
      "line_end": 308
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "就在笑腰穴下。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "若在笑腰穴附近，那就麻烦了。我实在不敢胡乱替你拔针，否则若是又一不小心，令那游丝针窜入你笑腰穴里，便是神仙也救不了的，只有眼看着你狂笑三日，笑死为止。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "既是如此，在下只有告辞，去另外设法了。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你现在若是随意走动，那游丝针也会跟你气血而动，窜入你笑腰穴里，你纵然十分小心，也走不出七十步的。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "贤夫妇的行径，的确令人难解得很，尊夫人不愿为人，却愿做马，这且不去说她，而阁下……",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 320
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你真的直到此刻还不知道我是谁？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 322,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "在下见识一向不广。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，移花宫门下，自然不会留意江湖侠踪……但十二星相这名字，你难道也从未听人说过？",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 328,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "不错，虎为山君，难怪阁下不但以虎自命，还蓄虎为奴，马为虎妻，难怪尊夫人不愿为人愿做马了。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你此刻既然已知道我是谁，便该知道十二星相中人，与移花宫乃是死敌，你既已落入我手中，难道不害怕么？",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "阁下若要动手，方才便不必救我，阁下方才既然救了我，想必是有求于我，阁下既然有求于我，我难道还会害怕么？",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "不错，我的确有求于你，只要你说出移花接玉这功夫的秘密，我不但立刻放了你，而且你若有所求，我必也件件应允。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 340,
      "line_end": 343
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "阁下若以为移花接玉的秘密，如此容易便可得到，阁下就未免会大大失望了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "你难道敢不说？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "speaker_name": "花无缺",
      "listener": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "text": "世上令人开口的法子有很多，有的以生死相胁，有的以酷刑逼供，有的以财色相诱，阁下不妨都试试看，看是否能令在下开口。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "我既然无法可想，也不愿白费气力，看来只有一走了之。你愿意留下，就留下，愿意走就走，我也管不了你了。不过你万一要找我时，只要大叫一声，我就会来的。",
      "tone": "平静",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_bai_shan_jun",
      "speaker_name": "白山君",
      "listener": "char_hua_wu_que",
      "text": "但你也莫要忘记，千万莫要走出七十步，否则大笑而死的滋味，可实在比什么死法都要难受得多。",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 79,
      "line_start": 358,
      "line_end": 358
    }
  ],
